metadata.name: _U_N_I_Q_U_E_
metadata.description:
_U_N_I_Q_U_E_ is a piece from the CASTLES MADE OF PIXELS series representing an inherent correlation between organically and digitally generated forms of life in regard to the unique individual properties they are composed of. These entities are castles made of pixels that slip into a decentralized sea of individuality, eventually.

Lasergun Factory (J. Scuderi) is a Digital/Crypto Artist from New York based in Tokyo with work found on ATO Platform, MakersPlace, Known Origin, Foundation, BAE, and, SuperRare. 

He has exhibited and spoken at various art and technology events including; CrypTOKYO, CAWA Japan, BOMA Artist Cafe, NFTxTOKYO, and The Great Reset /Small Reboots exhibition in Yokohama.
